Mwanza Youth and Children Network - MYCN shared a post.
3 May at 09:50

Today is World Press Freedom Day. Our Tanzanian Youth Reporters connect youth across the country to amplify their voices on important youth matters Children's Radio Foundation #WorldPressFreedom

+4
Wanahabari Vijana TZ - Youth Reporters TZ
3 May at 09:38

Leo tarehe 3 mwezi wa 5 ni siku ya uhuru wa vyombo vya habari duniani. Tunauganisha vijana toka mikoa mbalimbali hapa nchini kupaza sauti katika masuala nyeti y...a ustawi na maendeleo ya vijana. Kupitia wanahabari wetu waliopo katika mikoa ya Mwanza, Shinyanga, Dar-es-salaam, Zanzibar na Mbeya sauti za vijana hupazwa hewani. Kauli mbiu ya mwaka huu ni, Wajibu wa Uongozi, Vyombo vya Habari, Haki na Utawala wa Sheria
#WorldPressFreedom
